{"type":"section","nativeType":"section","number":"6683","heading":"Recognition program established","label":"6683 Recognition program established","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s6683","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t20/ch70/schII/ptB/spt5","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft20%2Fs6683","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":["Editorial Notes","CodificationSection was enacted as part of the Recognizing Achievement in Classified School Employees Act, and not as part of the Elementary and Secondary Education Act of 1965 which comprises this chapter."],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"a","heading":"In general","label":"a In general","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s6683/a","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t20/s6683","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft20%2Fs6683%2Fa","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The Secretary of Education shall establish a national recognition program to be known as the “Recognizing Inspiring School Employees Award Program” or the “award program”. The purpose of the award program shall be to recognize and promote the commitment and excellence exhibited by classified school employees who provide exemplary service to students in prekindergarten through high school.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"b","heading":"Award","label":"b Award","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s6683/b","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t20/s6683","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft20%2Fs6683%2Fb","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":"In general","label":"1 In general","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s6683/b/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t20/s6683/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft20%2Fs6683%2Fb%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"Prior to May 31 of each year (beginning with the second calendar year that begins after ), the Secretary shall select a classified school employee to receive the Recognizing Inspiring School Employees Award for the year.April 12, 2019","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":"Non-monetary value","label":"2 Non-monetary value","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s6683/b/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t20/s6683/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft20%2Fs6683%2Fb%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The award and recognition provided under this subpart shall have no monetary value.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"c","heading":"Selection process","label":"c Selection process","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s6683/c","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t20/s6683","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft20%2Fs6683%2Fc","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":"Nomination process","label":"1 Nomination process","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s6683/c/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t20/s6683/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft20%2Fs6683%2Fc%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":"In general","label":"A In general","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s6683/c/1/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t20/s6683/c/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft20%2Fs6683%2Fc%2F1%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"Not later than November 1 of each year (beginning with the first calendar year that begins after ), the Secretary shall solicit nominations of classified school employees from the occupational specialties described in from the Governor of each State.April 12, 2019section 6682(1) of this title","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":"Nomination submissions","label":"B Nomination submissions","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s6683/c/1/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t20/s6683/c/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft20%2Fs6683%2Fc%2F1%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"i","heading":null,"label":"i","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s6683/c/1/B/i","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t20/s6683/c/1/B","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft20%2Fs6683%2Fc%2F1%2FB%2Fi","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"Local educational agencies.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"ii","heading":null,"label":"ii","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s6683/c/1/B/ii","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t20/s6683/c/1/B","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft20%2Fs6683%2Fc%2F1%2FB%2Fii","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"School administrators.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"iii","heading":null,"label":"iii","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s6683/c/1/B/iii","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t20/s6683/c/1/B","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft20%2Fs6683%2Fc%2F1%2FB%2Fiii","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"Professional associations.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"iv","heading":null,"label":"iv","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s6683/c/1/B/iv","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t20/s6683/c/1/B","sourc